<h3 id="response">Response</h3>

<p>This is a <a href="#pagination">paginated collection</a>.
Responses will be contained inside a <code class="prettyprint">data</code> array, while metadata will be contained inside a <code class="prettyprint">meta</code> object.</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>id<br><em>string</em></td>
<td>Comment ID</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>name<br><em>string</em></td>
<td>Commenter name</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>text<br><em>string</em></td>
<td>Comment text</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>created_at<br><em>timestamp</em></td>
<td>When the comment was created</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
